high_descs: Turn to around and go towards the rug, when to the rug turn left and go towards the sinks
Pick up the soap holder between the two sinks.
Turn around and then turn back to your right and go right towards the toilet.
Put the soap holder on back of the toilet.
Turn back to your right, go forward and then left to face the sink.
Pick up another soap holder.
Turn left and go back towards the toilet
Put the soap holder on the back of the toilet as well.
Turn to your right and walk over to the sinks
Pick up the soap dispenser, in front of you, behind the cleaning bottle
Turn to your left and walk over to the toilet
Put the soap dispenser on top of the toilet tank, to the left of the candle
Turn to your right, then go over to the right sink
Open the bottom right cabinet and pick up another soap dispenser in the cabinet
Walk back over to the toilet to your left
Put the soap dispenser down, to the left of the other soap dispenser
anns.task_desc: Store two soap dispensers on the toilet tank

high_descs: turn around and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk over to the bathroom sink
grab the soap dispenser from the sink countertop
turn around and walk forwards a bit, then turn right over to the toilet
place the soap dispenser on top of the toilet
move to the right a bit and face the bathroom sink again
get the soap dispenser out from the cabinet to the bottom right of the right side sink
move back over to the toilet on the left next to the sink
place the soap dispenser next to the other soap dispenser on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place two soap dispensers on top of the toilet
